      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing function over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some typical wear and tear consistent with its age, such as minor oil seepage and a suspension that isn't quite as firm as it once was. The exterior shows some fading paint and several small dings, while the interior is clean but has visible wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go, though it would benefit from some preventative maintenance in the near future.",
