      "description": "Looking for a true diamond in the rough? This vehicle is the perfect project for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast ready to roll up their sleeves! While it currently requires significant mechanical work and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to bring a car back to life at a very budget-friendly price. If you love a challenge and have the skills to restore it, this could be your next great achievement!",
