      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or for parts. The exterior shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with fading paint and several body dents. Mechanically, the car requires significant repairs to be safely drivable, and the interior exhibits heavy wear, including torn seating and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is, with no guarantees on its roadworthiness.",
