      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a speed-sensitive M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on performance longevity, including a documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing service. Suspension geometry remains sharp with aluminum control arms and fresh bushings, providing the tactile feedback and turn-in precision this platform is known for. The exterior presents well with original body panels and functional aerodynamics, showing only minor cosmetic wear consistent with a well-kept driver\u2019s car. Mechanically robust and ready for the apex, this M3 represents a balanced example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a well-loved and meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. This car has been a reliable companion, consistently serviced on schedule to ensure the engine and transmission remain in smooth, responsive working order. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is clean and well-preserved, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. On the exterior, the body remains straight and the paint retains a healthy gloss, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips and light surface scuffs consistent with careful regular use. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension provides a composed, comfortable ride. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality driver that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers exceptional value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
